partnerDetails.about: Transform has an expansive range of over 5000 electrical product lines and is supplied by most leading local and internationally known manufacturers to this market. Our broad product range also includes distribution boards, cable, wire and accessories, industrial control gear, PLC's, Industrial and domestic lighting, circuit breakers, electricians tools, switches and plugs.
